cern.colt.buffer.tfloat
Class FloatBuffer2D

java.lang.Object
  cern.colt.PersistentObject
      cern.colt.buffer.tfloat.FloatBuffer2D
All Implemented Interfaces:
FloatBuffer2DConsumer, Serializable, Cloneable
public class FloatBuffer2D
extends PersistentObject
implements FloatBuffer2DConsumer

Fixed sized (non resizable) streaming buffer connected to a target FloatBuffer2DConsumer to which data is automatically flushed upon buffer overflow.

Version:
1.0, 09/24/99
Author:
wolfgang.hoschek@cern.ch
